# Valgrind suppressions for AI Agent.
#
# These silence known-benign noise from third-party libraries, NOT bugs in this
# codebase. Use with:  valgrind --suppressions=valgrind.supp ./agent ...
#
# OpenSSL's devcrypto engine probes /dev/crypto with an ioctl that reads a
# partially-uninitialised struct during OPENSSL_init_crypto (triggered via
# curl_global_init). Harmless, and entirely inside libcrypto.
{
   openssl-devcrypto-ioctl-uninitialised
   Memcheck:Param
   ioctl(generic)
   fun:ioctl
   ...
   obj:*/libcrypto.so.*
}
